<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KAN IN THANGTHAT KAN PATHIAN CH5</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan in thangthat, Pathian Kan lungthin le kan aw in, Khuaruahhar thil
 tuahtu, Vawlei mi nih an thangthat; Leicung kan chuahka in thluachuah a
 kan petu, Rel cawk lo dawtnak he Nihin ni tiang kan Pa.

[V2]
 Zeizong tlingmi Pathian, Kan sinah um zungzal tuah, Donglo lawmhnak
 thinlung, Daihnak he kan hnem ko tuah, Kan huppheng zungzal law kan hruai
 lam kan tlau ah, Lei le vancung zongah, Temhnak in kan luat-ter.

[V3]
 Thangthat lawmhnak vialte, Kan Pa Pathian pe ko u, Amah sin a ummi
 Fapa le Thiangthlarau he, Zungzal hmunmi Pathian lei le van nih biakmi,
 Zungzal in zungzal tiang A hmun zungzal ko lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<hymn_number>5</hymn_number>
</song>